(73, '1482944016.', 'Barish me basee lamho ki dastak', 'Pr wo akhein kabhi ye samjhte nahi ...', 'Sham ki hatheli pe barish ki tanhai,\r\nJaha ishq bezubaan ha leke badalo ki parchaiâ€¦\r\nShishe pe likhe taqdir ka rang jab sachai se leti ha rishwat,\r\nBadalo me chupe suraj ke sang tab barish deti ha dastakâ€¦\r\nDin me chaye andhere me lamho ki ha shikayat,\r\nPani me dube huye rah me,chahat ki ha ibadatâ€¦\r\nYe dil dharakna chahta ha kisi or k liye roshni ki khwab lekar,\r\nPar wo akhe kabhi ye samajhte nahi gujre huye waqt ki dua ban karâ€¦'),
