(84, '1482945737.jpg', 'When together we are...', 'Dreams of The Anarchy!', 'The time you feel lonely is the time you most need to be by yourself.'),
(85, '1482945821.jpg', 'Day of Night', 'Nature of Time', 'Night turns Day and Day turns Night,\r\nNever mind my theory, just makes guide.\r\nLittle bit of Ray is the cause of Light,\r\nAnd a little bit of Light is the end of Night!\r\n\r\nThe similar way the Dark makes path,\r\nTypical mind makes the timing rough.\r\nDawn comes in way to end Dark thus,\r\nFight of Love gets victory with rush.\r\n\r\nThanks for Reading this Lines of Mine,\r\nKeep Making Joy and Happiness by Shine.'),
