(93, '1482946766.jpg', 'Day of Independence', 'The day of Freedom...', 'Forget not that the grossest crime is to compromise with injustice and wrong. Remember the eternal law: you must give, if you want to get. - Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose\r\n\r\nRevolution is an inalienable right of mankind. Freedom is an imperishable birth right of all. Labour is the real sustainer of society, the sovereignty of the ultimate destiny of the workers. - Bhagat Singh'),
