(104, '1482948308.jpg', 'Christmas Eve with some Cake...', 'Merry Christmas', 'Christmas! Christmas! Santa came on dream,\r\nLiteral thoughts are making mind clean!\r\nNicholas is on the ride, with toys and gifts,\r\nRudolph gets above the Moon and lightened firs.\r\n\r\nDrifter of Real time never leaves clock,\r\nReindeer are on the run, surpassing every block.\r\nLiving by the North Pole, the Saint of Myra,\r\nLove of the little children, tells "sayonara".\r\n\r\nBirthday of Jesus feels, have some cake!\r\nMouth gets cold enough to make some shake.\r\nThis is called the great day where night is long,\r\nLittle brains, growing minds â€“ dont take it wrong!\r\n\r\nHoliday is saying God, â€œPlay your Showâ€,\r\nSanta be like hearing that, "ho! ho! ho!"\r\n');
